                            <h3>Exercise</h3>
<p>Run ls with different flags and see the output you receive.</p>

                        </div>

                        <div class="quiz-content">
                            <h3>Quiz Question</h3>
<p>What command would you use to see hidden files?</p>
<h3>Quiz Answer</h3>
<p>ls -a</p>
